The second largest city in the northern Mexican State of Sonora and is situated 525 km south of the state's border with the State of Arizona. It is also the municipal seat of Cajeme municipality, located in the Yaqui Valley.

One of the regions (mintaqah) of Oman. Adh Dhahirah region consists of three wilayats: Ibri, Yanqul, and Dank. Until 2006-10, two more wilayats were part of the region: Al Buraymi and Mahdah. In 2006-10, a new governorate, Al Buraymi was created from these two wilayats, and a third wilayat, Al Sinaihah was created from parts of the two.
